<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>GroupJuke</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" type="text/css" media="screen" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap-responsive.min.css" type="text/css" media="screen" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css" type="text/css" media="screen" />
    
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <div id="main" class="container">

      <header class="jumbotron subhead" id="overview">
        <h1>GroupJuke</h1>
        <p class="lead">Democratize your playlist.</p>

        <div class="panelcollapsed">
          <h2>How-To</h2>
          <div class="panelcontent">
            <p class="first">Use this site for playing music in room full of people. (A party, for example.) </p>
            <p>As the music plays, everyone can help decide which track will play next by <strong>voting</strong> for the song they want to hear next.</p>
            <p>Vote by texting in two things:
              <ol>
                <li>The <strong>Instance Code</strong> (the two-character code displayed below).</li>
                <li>The <strong>Song Number</strong> (1, 2, 3, or 4).</li>
              </ol>
            </p>
            <p>For example, text "<span class="appcode">4A</span>-1" to vote for song 1.</p>
            <p>Vote as many times as you want!</p>
            <p>When the current song ends, the song with the most votes will automatically play next. Then a new random crop of songs will appear to vote on.</p>
            <p>Click â–¶ on the music player to get started with a randomly chosen first song.</p>
            <p>What plays next is up to the crowd!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </header>

      <div class="page-header">
          <p class="lead">Text your vote here:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><small class="phone-number">+1 714-294-2347</small></li>
          </ul>

          <p class="lead">Instance Code:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><small class="appcode phone-number"></small></li>
          </ul>

          <p class="lead">Example:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><small class="phone-number">Text "<span class="appcode"></span>-1" to vote for song choice 1</small></li>
          </ul>

      </div>

      <div class="music-player">
        <p><small id="currplaying">Currently Playing: </small><span id="currSongTitle"></span></p>
        <audio id="player" src="" controls></audio>
      </div>
      
      <div class="row">    

        <div class="span8">
          <p class="lead">Next Song Choices:</p>
          <ul id="song_choices">
            <li id="song1obj"><span class="num">1</span> <span id="song1title" class="songTitle">Song 1</span>
              <div>Votes: <span id="votes" class="song1votes">0</span></div></li>
            <li id="song2obj"><span class="num">2</span> <span id="song2title" class="songTitle">Song 2</span>
              <div>Votes: <span id="votes" class="song2votes">0</span></div></li>
            <li id="song3obj"><span class="num">3</span> <span id="song3title" class="songTitle">Song 3</span>
              <div>Votes: <span id="votes" class="song3votes">0</span></div></li>
            <li id="song4obj"><span class="num">4</span> <span id="song4title" class="songTitle">Song 4</span>
              <div>Votes: <span id="votes" class="song4votes">0</span></div></li>
          </ul>
          <p><small>Powered by <a href="http://pusher.com">Pusher</a> &amp; <a href="http://twilio.com">Twilio</a>. <em>Use me in a modern browser that supports HTML5 audio!</em></small></p>
        </div>

        <div class="span3">
          <p class="lead">Live Vote Feed:</p>
          <ul id="sms_messages"></ul>
        </div>
      
      </div>



    </div>
    
    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.7.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://js.pusher.com/1.12/pusher.min.js"></script>
    <script>
      var PUSHER_CONFIG = {
        APP_KEY: '<%= @app_key %>'
      };
    </script>
    <script src="js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="js/test_helpers.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/utils.js"></script>


  </body>
</html>